391
00:30:41,967 --> 00:30:43,510
You make me ashamed to be British.

392
00:30:43,594 --> 00:30:45,428
All right. Come on. Let's step away.
Step away.

393
00:30:45,429 --> 00:30:47,264
Back up. Back up. Back up. Good man.

394
00:30:52,811 --> 00:30:54,646
