that First Desk, Ingrid Tearney, will be debriefing the Home Secretary later on today on what has been a successful operation to rescue kidnapped student Hassan Ahmed.

441
00:36:00,494 --> 00:36:10,504
[Hassan] I'd just like to say thank you to the police a-and the security services for their really, really incredible work.

442
00:36:11,004 --> 00:36:20,597
We understand he was freed
shortly after 7:00 a.m. this morning by an MI5 operation in which two of the kidnappers were killed, and a further man remains in custody.

443
00:36:24,560 --> 00:36:27,228
